{"tid":966862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奶共香港主教楊嗚章死左","createTime":"2019-01-03T06:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T10:50:41.000Z","uid":134683,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bae42313aaa898ffb9e12e66756618bd02702652","tid":966862,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"下個到教宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/share/156327\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fshare%2F156327&d=PZ3qdoSPo8vHT0mRLP2TsTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c29596f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/share/156327</a>"},{"pid":"9321dde502675febc24f86152f46c1e209ac6670","tid":966862,"uid":134683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T06:22:36.000Z","msg":"楊鳴章病逝 終年73歲<br />\n<br />\n26 分前<br />\n<br />\n#Hashtags<br />\n<br />\n楊鳴章天主教<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n楊鳴章<br />\n<br />\n天主教香港教區主教楊鳴章逝世，終年73歲。天主教社會傳播處今日較早前發出新聞稿，證實楊鳴章因肝硬化致肝衰竭入院的消息，但當時仍指楊鳴章情況穩定。<br />\n楊鳴章上一次公開露面是在上月的聖誕節在堅道主教座堂主持子夜彌撒，楊鳴章上月亦有透過影片發表聖誕賀辭，呼籲教徒在堂區、學校、家庭以至個人層面，接觸最少一位有需要的人士或一個家庭，為他們祈禱。"},{"pid":"70c80e883d66cdd2ec2ec42fb46b4fd3a486fa48","tid":966862,"uid":7206,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T06:25:32.000Z","msg":"奶共神棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蒙毛主席寵召<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdda1ad4dd8060842e115aee1c8a15bacd75c04","tid":966862,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T06:26:45.000Z","msg":"去見毛主席呀五毛"},{"pid":"cbb2aa4b5a3f833c18c9b0ca0099ea04bdde2236","tid":966862,"uid":19126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T06:44:37.000